TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Intelligence confirms that the enemy has left behind a vast energy production facility on the southern plane. We believe it is deserted but guarded by strong defensive towers. Find the facility and destory it! You have 10 minutes.

TriggerLogic.Name: Marker
TriggerLogic.Text: You'll need a big army of tanks to destroy the enemy defence.
Expand your base as fast as you can and cap all nearby metal spots.
Once you are producing lots of resources, then make a lab and produce units quickly.
This is a nanolathe. Set it to patrol and it will help nearby construction/factories.
You can build nanolathes with any tech 1 constructor.
It's important to use the right kind of unit.
This is an advanced solar collector. It produces lots of energy but also costs lots of energy to build.
Adv solar collectors can be built by any tech 1 constructor.

TriggerLogic.Name: Marker
TriggerLogic.Text: In this mission, you'll be using vehicles instead of kbots.

TriggerLogic.Name: Marker
TriggerLogic.Text: To destroy defensive towers, tanks will work better than artillery or missile trucks.
